msgstr "Ventana individual"

#: src/appfinder-preferences.glade:242
msgid ""
"When an instance is running in the background, only open one window at a "
"time."
msgstr "Cuandu haya una istancia executándose nel fondu, abrir una ventana nueva al tiempo namái."

